cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with video frame interpolation, which is a computer vision problem, hence the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper experiments with different loss functions, which could also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
